 O people of vision.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقال عز وجل \"وظنوا أنهم ما نعتهم حصونهم من الله فأتاهم الله من حيث لم يحتسبوا\" فرد على الكفار في أعجابهم بحصونهم وشوكتهم\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, He, the Mighty and Majestic, said: \"And they thought that their fortresses [ḥuṣūn] would protect them from Allah. But Allah came to them from where they did not expect.\" Thus, He refuted the disbelievers in their pride [aʿjāb] regarding their fortresses and their might [shawka].\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.8","c":"وَلَوْلَا","d":"walawlā","e":"walawlā"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.69","c":"أَنْ","d":"an","e":"an"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.87","c":"كَتَبَ","d":"kataba","e":"kataba"},{"b":"3.8","h":"6","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"l-lahu"},{"b":"4.5","h":"7.44","c":"عَلَيْهِمُ","d":"ʿalayhimu","e":"ʿalayhimu"},{"b":"5.6","h":"9.21","c":"الْجَلَاءَ","d":"l-jalāa","e":"l-jalāa"},{"b":"7.7","h":"11.69","c":"لَعَذَّبَهُمْ","d":"laʿadhabahum","e":"laʿadhabahum"},{"b":"9.0","h":"14.05","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"9.3","h":"14.45","c":"الدُّنْيَا","d":"l-dun'yā","e":"l-dun'yā"},{"b":"10.8","h":"18.21","c":"وَلَهُمْ","d":"walahum","e":"walahum"},{"b":"11.5","h":"19.39","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"11.8","h":"19.75","c":"الْءَاخِرَةِ","d":"l-ākhirati","e":"l-ākhirati"},{"b":"12.9","h":"21.79","c":"عَذَابُ","d":"ʿadhābu","e":"ʿadhābu"},{"b":"13.6","h":"23.57","c":"النَّارِ","d":"l-nāri","e":"l-nāri"}],"a":{"g":"And if not that Allah had decreed for